    <p> Now we need to write our other factor as a sum of powers of two. For example,
      <m> 7 = 1 + 2 + 4 = 2^0 + 2^1 + 2^2</m>.
    </p>

    <question xml:id="ques-twos2">
      <title>Powers of 2 to get 12</title>
      <statement>
        <p>
          Write 12 as a sum of powers of 2.
        </p>
      </statement>
      <solution>
        <p>
          <m>12 = 4 + 8 = 2^2 + 2^3 </m>
        </p>
      </solution>      
      
    </question>

